Raw Text:
Stricken language would be deleted from and underlined language would be added to present law.
Act 984 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 HOUSE BILL 1984
4
5 By: Representatives Hudson, Evans, Gazaway
6 By: Senators B. Davis, J. Scott
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO CREATE A DESIGNATION FOR A REGISTERED SEX
10 OFFENDER ON A DRIVER'S LICENSE OR IDENTIFICATION
11 CARD; TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING THE SEX OFFENDER
12 REGISTRATION ACT OF 1997; TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING
13 THE ISSUANCE OF LICENSES AND PERMITS; AND FOR OTHER
14 PURPOSES.
