Subtitle
17
18 TO CREATE A DESIGNATION FOR A REGISTERED
19 SEX OFFENDER ON A DRIVER'S LICENSE OR
20 IDENTIFICATION CARD.
21
22 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
23
24 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 12-12-913(a), concerning a disclosure of a
25 person's status as a registered sex offender, is amended to add an additional
26 subdivision read as follows:
27 (4) Registration records shall be open to the Office of Motor
28 Vehicle of the Department of Finance and Administration for the issuance of a
29 driver's license or identification card to a registered sex offender under §
30 27-16-819.
31
32 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code Title 27, Chapter 16, Subchapter 8, is
33 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
34 27-16-819. Designation for registered sex offender.
35 (a)(1) Before the Office of Driver Services issues a driver's license
36 or identification card to an applicant, the applicant shall provide
